  "description": "A white and grey bird in flight, likely a gull, dominates the frame against a pale grey, overcast sky. The bird is captured mid-wingbeat, with its wings fully extended and slightly angled upwards. The bird's plumage is primarily white, transitioning to grey on the wingtips. A vibrant yellow beak and hints of pink at the underside of the wing add splashes of color. The overall composition highlights the bird's dynamic movement and aerial grace.",
